Step 3 evaluation: Yes - The third position ($10k compromise) is claimed to be correct only because it is a compromise between the other two positions, despite the assumption that the car is actually worth $20k
Pattern comparison: My answers [Y/Y/Y] exactly match ground truth [Y/Y/Y]
